1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
English subtitles are available.

2
00:00:00,780 --> 00:00:03,220
I've decided no matter what you say.

3
00:00:03,220 --> 00:00:06,450
Yuki, what the hell do you want?

4
00:00:06,690 --> 00:00:08,119
Good morning.

5
00:00:08,520 --> 00:00:12,020
I also had something to ask Miss Risa as well.

6
00:00:12,360 --> 00:00:13,430
Okay.

7
00:00:13,690 --> 00:00:17,460
Please let me live here with the both of you.

8
00:00:24,940 --> 00:00:26,710
I'm not going to ask you anything.

9
00:00:27,440 --> 00:00:29,070
Stay as long as you want.

10
00:00:31,340 --> 00:00:32,640
Are you sure?

11
00:00:36,280 --> 00:00:40,390
I might end up ruining your relationship.

12
00:00:42,920 --> 00:00:44,620
Do whatever you wish.

13
00:00:50,760 --> 00:00:53,330
Yuki, please stop.

14
00:00:53,730 --> 00:00:58,340
You can't stop me, Ms. Risa.

15
00:00:58,340 --> 00:01:00,640
Yuki, stop it already.

16
00:01:02,710 --> 00:01:05,209
- I'm in charge of breakfast.
- It's already done.

17
00:01:05,209 --> 00:01:06,980
- What?
- What's going on?

18
00:01:08,650 --> 00:01:13,150
I'm a freeloader, so I should be taking care of the housework.

19
00:01:13,150 --> 00:01:15,620
Yuki, you don't need to do anything.

20
00:01:15,620 --> 00:01:18,860
Risa, just let him be. Besides...

21
00:01:19,730 --> 00:01:24,760
Since you're calling him by his first name, why don't you do the same for me?

22
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:30,140
Call me Hiroto.

23
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:38,440
Hiroto...

24
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:44,680
Maybe you could call me Hiroto after becoming Mrs. Fukami.

25
00:01:46,550 --> 00:01:48,690
What do you think, Yuki?

26
00:01:50,320 --> 00:01:51,820
How do I know?

27
00:01:54,229 --> 00:01:57,100
He must be dumbfounded.

28
00:02:01,930 --> 00:02:03,740
Coffee & Vanilla

29
00:02:39,740 --> 00:02:44,710
[Episode 9 Risk & Danger]

30
00:02:44,410 --> 00:02:46,810
Boss, here is your coffee.

31
00:02:46,810 --> 00:02:47,910
Thanks.

32
00:02:48,750 --> 00:02:50,320
Boss, your tie is crooked.

33
00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:54,990
He could be a better wife than me.

34
00:02:58,860 --> 00:03:03,200
Excuse me. I'll cook supper tonight.

35
00:03:03,460 --> 00:03:05,560
- How about a hamburg steak?
- Sounds good.

36
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:08,470
He has a dinner meeting in the evening.

37
00:03:08,470 --> 00:03:10,900
So you should prepare a light supper.

38
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,970
I can cook dinner too.

39
00:03:12,970 --> 00:03:14,910
No, I will cook.

40
00:03:18,980 --> 00:03:22,910
I'm so incompetent.

41
00:03:24,620 --> 00:03:28,620
I still have a lot to learn to become Fukami's future wife.

42
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:33,260
Yuki is more capable than me.

43
00:03:35,090 --> 00:03:37,360
No! Don't be so negative.

44
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:39,870
Sulking won't change anything. I have to improve.

45
00:03:48,110 --> 00:03:50,880
Yuki, you're back.

46
00:03:51,140 --> 00:03:52,740
Is she your acquaintance?

47
00:03:53,380 --> 00:03:55,010
Yes, sort of.

48
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:59,020
I'm sorry. I didn't know you're working now.

49
00:03:59,020 --> 00:04:00,190
Well...

50
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:04,990
The director of the Queen Coffee who has been our good business partner.

51
00:04:04,990 --> 00:04:06,360
Mrs. Megumi.

52
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:08,160
Director?

53
00:04:08,330 --> 00:04:11,860
How am I supposed to introduce myself?

54
00:04:11,860 --> 00:04:14,430
Should I tell her that I'm Mr. Fukami's girlfriend?

55
00:04:15,330 --> 00:04:16,839
I...

56
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:19,670
She is my cousin.

57
00:04:19,670 --> 00:04:21,610
Is she?

58
00:04:23,740 --> 00:04:25,110
Right.

59
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:26,980
I'll be going now.

60
00:04:26,980 --> 00:04:29,310
Please say hello to CEO Fukami for me.

61
00:04:30,020 --> 00:04:31,280
Take care.

62
00:04:40,159 --> 00:04:43,030
I'm sorry for telling her you're my cousin.

63
00:04:46,700 --> 00:04:48,230
It's fine.

64
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:54,540
What a wonderful lady.

65
00:04:55,940 --> 00:04:58,340
It's amazing that she's a director.

66
00:04:59,909 --> 00:05:03,280
She is the director of the Queen Coffee,

67
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:05,180
also the wife of the CEO.

68
00:05:07,150 --> 00:05:09,960
Is that so?

69
00:05:12,460 --> 00:05:16,090
I don't want to spoil your fun living with him, but

70
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:21,930
what advantages do you have for being his fiancée?

71
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,710
Please give a serious thought about that.

72
00:05:36,350 --> 00:05:38,720
Risa, aren't you going to sleep?

73
00:05:39,080 --> 00:05:42,490
I have to finish my report.

74
00:05:42,490 --> 00:05:45,890
- You can go to sleep first.
- Okay.

75
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:53,170
Did something happen with Yuki?

76
00:05:56,570 --> 00:06:00,110
No. Why do you ask?

77
00:06:00,310 --> 00:06:01,240
Nothing.

78
00:06:02,970 --> 00:06:06,950
You know, I have to go on a business trip tomorrow.

79
00:06:10,620 --> 00:06:14,490
Okay. Have a nice trip.

80
00:06:15,050 --> 00:06:18,920
Good night. Good luck with your report.

81
00:06:21,130 --> 00:06:22,430
Good night.

82
00:06:27,770 --> 00:06:32,670
The truth is, I wish he hugs me tight.

83
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:36,940
And tells me everything is fine.

84
00:06:41,350 --> 00:06:45,620
But, I can't improve when he pampers me like that.

85
00:06:50,420 --> 00:06:54,630
Aren't you going to comfort her as always?

86
00:06:57,700 --> 00:07:01,230
Or, are you going to kick me out?

87
00:07:03,940 --> 00:07:07,170
I told you to do whatever you wish.

88
00:07:07,810 --> 00:07:09,810
If Ms. Risa gets hurt,

89
00:07:10,810 --> 00:07:12,640
she might give up on you.

90
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:16,210
The woman I love isn't that weak.

91
00:07:17,380 --> 00:07:21,690
I won't comfort her unless she wishes me to.

92
00:07:28,990 --> 00:07:33,270
Boss, I need to tell you something.

93
00:07:39,340 --> 00:07:42,010
Yuki, you're not going with him?

94
00:07:42,310 --> 00:07:45,010
No, I have to take care of businesses here.

95
00:07:47,010 --> 00:07:49,310
Then, I'm off.

96
00:07:50,550 --> 00:07:53,550
Ms. Risa, where are you going to today?

97
00:07:56,690 --> 00:07:59,159
I'm going to a job interview for an intern position.

98
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:02,090
After hearing your suggestions,

99
00:08:02,090 --> 00:08:04,430
I want to improve myself.

100
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:09,330
But I can only take a small step.

101
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:15,340
Could you not tell Fukami about this? See you.

102
00:08:16,170 --> 00:08:17,840
I'll drive you there.

103
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:21,150
I'm fine. I can go alone.

104
00:08:21,150 --> 00:08:22,310
I'm off.

105
00:08:34,289 --> 00:08:35,960
Yuki?

106
00:08:35,990 --> 00:08:37,530
I'll escort you.

107
00:08:37,530 --> 00:08:40,700
I told you I'm fine.

108
00:08:41,429 --> 00:08:45,700
He must think I'm so incapable.

109
00:08:47,470 --> 00:08:48,670
Ms. Risa.

110
00:08:57,380 --> 00:09:00,350
Thank you.

111
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:10,300
Yuki?

112
00:09:11,630 --> 00:09:13,300
Sorry.

113
00:09:15,370 --> 00:09:19,070
You should be more aware of your surroundings.

114
00:09:20,940 --> 00:09:23,040
Don't put your guard down.

115
00:09:24,010 --> 00:09:25,340
I know.

116
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:29,650
His behavior was odd.

117
00:09:30,420 --> 00:09:34,390
- Let's go.
- Okay.

118
00:09:34,390 --> 00:09:37,490
His secretary and the girlfriend? That can't be true.

119
00:09:37,490 --> 00:09:40,160
But I saw them.

120
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:42,690
His girlfriend is Fukami's weakness.

121
00:09:42,690 --> 00:09:45,860
- Don't screw this up.
- Yes, sir.

