00:09:49,970 --> 00:09:53,240
[We are sorry to inform you that,
you have not been selected for the position.
We would like to thank you again for choosing us among the many companies, 
and we wish you all the best.]

124
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:56,740
I didn't expect to be hired in my first interview.

125
00:10:06,650 --> 00:10:08,320
Hello?

126
00:10:08,790 --> 00:10:14,190
Hello? May I speak with Shiragi Risa ?

127
00:10:15,490 --> 00:10:16,660
Speaking.

128
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:20,670
I'm calling from the HR Department of South Entertainment.

129
00:10:23,940 --> 00:10:25,570
Oh, hello.

130
00:10:25,770 --> 00:10:28,770
After much deliberation,

131
00:10:28,770 --> 00:10:32,080
we'd like you to join our internship program.

132
00:10:35,010 --> 00:10:38,050
- What?
- I'm sorry.

133
00:10:38,050 --> 00:10:41,890
My co-worker sent you the wrong e-mail.

134
00:10:42,530 --> 00:10:45,440
Miss Risa, are you going to the interview today too?

135
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:49,680
Actually, I was accepted into the internship.

136
00:10:51,980 --> 00:10:55,680
I'm going to the induction today.

137
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:00,690
Yuki?

138
00:11:08,790 --> 00:11:11,960
I'm the guardian of Shiragi Risa

139
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:16,130
who is going to be your intern.

140
00:11:20,640 --> 00:11:23,410
I have sent her e-mail to notify

141
00:11:23,410 --> 00:11:25,940
that she wasn't selected.

142
00:11:26,450 --> 00:11:29,950
Is that right? We must've missed the e-mail.

143
00:11:29,950 --> 00:11:32,480
Sorry to bother you.

144
00:11:32,950 --> 00:11:37,920
The person who called you is one of the schemers against the Boss.

145
00:11:40,290 --> 00:11:44,200
Boss is taking care of them by now.

146
00:11:44,500 --> 00:11:46,160
Mr. Fukami?

147
00:11:47,070 --> 00:11:51,400
You have wasted his time to deal with your trivial matter.

148
00:11:54,170 --> 00:12:00,610
I told you not to put your guard down.

149
00:12:02,910 --> 00:12:06,020
You're so naive, Ms. Risa.

150
00:12:11,560 --> 00:12:13,630
If you say that you let him go,

151
00:12:13,630 --> 00:12:17,360
I won't hurt you.

152
00:12:19,770 --> 00:12:25,470
I'm capable of harming you physically and mentally.

153
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:33,050
I will do anything to make you give up.

154
00:12:40,150 --> 00:12:41,920
I won't give up!

155
00:12:46,190 --> 00:12:51,630
Mr. Fukami protected even someone like me.

156
00:12:52,260 --> 00:12:54,970
And, he thinks of our future.

157
00:12:56,200 --> 00:12:58,540
I won't lose!

158
00:13:01,270 --> 00:13:03,580
Right now, I'm just being protected, but...

159
00:13:06,450 --> 00:13:09,750
I'll become strong! Strong enough to even protect Mr. Fukami.

160
00:13:13,620 --> 00:13:16,460
Because no matter how much you oppose me, I will continue to love him!

161
00:13:24,360 --> 00:13:25,560
Is that so?

162
00:13:28,730 --> 00:13:31,700
Well then, you pass.

163
00:13:33,970 --> 00:13:35,210
Huh?

164
00:13:36,140 --> 00:13:38,910
Please forgive my brazenness up until now.

165
00:13:43,380 --> 00:13:45,750
Mr. Yuki, please stop.

166
00:13:47,820 --> 00:13:51,960
No matter what, I wanted to tell you about

167
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:55,030
the trials you will be facing from here on out.

168
00:13:57,460 --> 00:14:02,700
There will be people who try to get in your way of your relationship.

169
00:14:02,930 --> 00:14:06,100
They might try to do even more cruel things than I did.

170
00:14:06,570 --> 00:14:08,710
Before it comes to that,

171
00:14:09,510 --> 00:14:14,080
I wanted to know how prepared you are.

172
00:14:17,250 --> 00:14:20,750
If we let them think I'm your lover instead of the boss,

173
00:14:20,750 --> 00:14:22,790
I thought that I could keep things in check.

174
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:26,360
Ms. Risa.

175
00:14:28,990 --> 00:14:33,770
Even though it was to protect you, please forgive me.

176
00:14:37,470 --> 00:14:42,310
Mr. Yuki, thank you.

177
00:14:45,180 --> 00:14:47,510
Thanks to you,

178
00:14:49,610 --> 00:14:53,120
I matured a little.

179
00:14:57,860 --> 00:14:59,960
That's just like you, Ms. Risa.

180
00:15:02,330 --> 00:15:05,200
- I'm back.
- Welcome back.

181
00:15:05,560 --> 00:15:09,170
- Where's Risa?
- She went to bed already.

182
00:15:10,870 --> 00:15:13,270
I've taken measures against them.

183
00:15:13,270 --> 00:15:15,940
And leaked information about the embezzlement affair.

184
00:15:15,940 --> 00:15:17,710
What a horrifying thing to do...

185
00:15:17,710 --> 00:15:20,180
It's because they were targeting Risa that it came to this.

186
00:15:22,550 --> 00:15:25,650
I apologize for my lack of ability.

187
00:15:30,760 --> 00:15:35,390
Thank you, Yuki, for protecting Risa.

188
00:15:37,830 --> 00:15:39,430
Of course.

189
00:15:41,030 --> 00:15:43,100
She's someone important to you, after all.

190
00:15:50,110 --> 00:15:51,410
Boss...

191
00:15:52,280 --> 00:15:54,310
You hugged Risa, didn't you?

192
00:15:55,210 --> 00:15:58,150
I wanted to cancel out the feeling that Risa left on you.

193
00:16:04,460 --> 00:16:10,200
You thought that Risa and I...?

194
00:16:10,860 --> 00:16:11,860
There's no way.

195
00:16:13,230 --> 00:16:16,970
That's because the person that you like is me, isn't it?

196
00:16:17,400 --> 00:16:19,600
You're unbelievable...

197
00:16:23,940 --> 00:16:28,310
I'll go prepare the car, so please take your time.

198
00:16:29,920 --> 00:16:31,220
Okay.

199
00:16:35,890 --> 00:16:37,160
Risa.

200
00:16:40,490 --> 00:16:41,560
Come here.

201
00:16:44,260 --> 00:16:47,200
Uh, but...

202
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:48,430
Come on, hurry up.

203
00:17:06,819 --> 00:17:10,260
Seeing you in a suit is also quite fascinating, Risa.

204
00:17:10,690 --> 00:17:13,290
Stop, we need to go.

205
00:17:27,470 --> 00:17:30,340
That's a mark that says we'll be together forever.

206
00:17:43,060 --> 00:17:46,890
I want to keep you in my arms forever, like this.

207
00:17:49,030 --> 00:17:53,370
Then, even if it becomes painful for you to be with me,

208
00:17:53,570 --> 00:17:54,830
or you try to escape,

209
00:17:56,230 --> 00:17:58,600
I can just lock you up by this.

210
00:18:04,140 --> 00:18:07,710
Sorry, what am I saying?

211
00:18:16,660 --> 00:18:21,160
It's fine. I won't run away.

212
00:18:22,230 --> 00:18:27,800
I'll stay with you forever. Whatever happens.

213
00:18:41,080 --> 00:18:44,020
I was told to contact him back.

214
00:18:45,550 --> 00:18:47,750
I definitely want you to eat a hamburg steak today

215
00:18:48,250 --> 00:18:50,290
A delicious hamburg steak

216
00:18:50,290 --> 00:18:51,820
that even Mr. Yuki would approve of.

217
00:18:52,860 --> 00:18:54,960
Um... Excuse me.

218
00:19:07,830 --> 00:19:10,860
You didn't realize that you were being targeted?

219
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:15,030
Even though you're Fukami's woman...

220
00:19:21,370 --> 00:19:24,310
I was hired to do this, you know.

221
00:19:24,740 --> 00:19:27,180
Someone told me to get you,

222
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:30,620
and give Mr. Fukami a hard time.

223
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:36,020
How much will he pay for you I wonder?

224
00:19:36,020 --> 00:19:41,260
50 million yen? No, 100 million yen.

225
00:19:46,830 --> 00:19:48,430
Stop it!

226
00:19:48,430 --> 00:19:51,770
Well then, I guess I'll have you pay with your body.

227
00:19:54,010 --> 00:19:58,580
There will be people who try to get in your way of your relationship.

228
00:19:58,580 --> 00:20:01,250
They might try to do even more cruel things than I did.

229
00:20:03,950 --> 00:20:08,520
Right now, I'm just being protected, but...

230
00:20:08,520 --> 00:20:10,590
I'll become strong! Strong enough to even protect Mr. Fukami.

231
00:20:14,660 --> 00:20:17,660
What? Are you up for this?

232
00:20:26,970 --> 00:20:29,510
There's no way you could get even a mere 100 million yen.

233
00:20:33,280 --> 00:20:35,080
Get away from Risa.

234
00:20:37,220 --> 00:20:40,350
Stay back, I'll stab her!

235
00:20:41,250 --> 00:20:44,660
Stay back! I'll stab her!

236
00:20:50,230 --> 00:20:52,830
Give Risa back to me!

237
00:20:57,370 --> 00:20:59,500
Sorry I'm late Risa.

238
00:20:59,970 --> 00:21:01,010
Are you ok?

239
00:21:01,010 --> 00:21:02,770
Mr. Fukami, your hand!

240
00:21:02,770 --> 00:21:03,840
It's fine.

241
00:21:05,510 --> 00:21:08,750
No, I won't get arrested!

242
00:21:08,750 --> 00:21:11,550
- Get out of my way!
- Mr. Fukami!

243
00:21:15,950 --> 00:21:20,160
He'll be fine, the injury isn't very bad, apparently.

244
00:21:20,960 --> 00:21:22,630
It was all my fault.

245
00:21:23,800 --> 00:21:25,530
It's not your fault, Ms. Risa.

246
00:21:39,810 --> 00:21:42,410
It was just as Mr. Yuki said.

247
00:21:45,850 --> 00:21:49,520
It's fine. I won't run away.

248
00:21:49,890 --> 00:21:55,930
I'll stay with you forever. No matter what happens.

249
00:21:59,230 --> 00:22:01,830
Even though I said those things...

250
00:22:02,830 --> 00:22:05,400
I couldn't do anything for Mr. Fukami.

251
00:22:06,040 --> 00:22:09,410
It's always Mr. Fukami that sacrifices himself.

252
00:22:10,140 --> 00:22:15,480
It's all my fault for being so useless.

253
00:22:23,050 --> 00:22:25,120
How can I be good enough for him?

254
00:22:42,370 --> 00:22:43,410
Risa?

255
00:23:00,160 --> 00:23:01,890
Dear Fukami,

256
00:23:04,030 --> 00:23:06,260
I can't stay with you any longer.

257
00:23:08,100 --> 00:23:09,500
I'm truly...

258
00:23:15,470 --> 00:23:16,810
sorry.

259
00:23:45,070 --> 00:23:48,140
I want he to be happy, so we can't see each other anymore.

260
00:23:48,140 --> 00:23:49,610
It's Risa's decision.

261
00:23:49,610 --> 00:23:51,410
Are you going to give up so easily?

262
00:23:51,410 --> 00:23:53,610
The rest is up to him to decide.

263
00:23:53,610 --> 00:23:55,180
